Been a dream of ours to stay at @turtlebayresort with our fam since Jack said the word “woah” 🚁. If you’ve been following me for a long time you know exactly what I’m talking about lol…BUT if you’re new we used to take Jack almost every day to the beach & to see the helicopters take off from turtle bay when we lived on the island. It became our family’s most memorable place:) Jack still carries around his little helicopter pin with him & has it sleep next to his bed. His 1st birthday theme was about the turtle bay woahs (helicopters). If you think that’s extreme just know that Derik also sings him a 10 min made up song about turtle bay when he goes to bed every night hahaha. So glad we made some of the best memories there together this last week🥲💛 it was everything we thought it would be! #onlyatturtlebay
